<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.2">
<l>kalaṅka mākkaṭa larikulam paṇiceyya</l>
<l>varuvarai yaṇaikaṭṭi</l>
<l>ilaṅkai mānakarp poṭiceyta vaṭikaḷtā</l>
<l>miruntanal limayattu</l>
<l>vilaṅkaṟ pōlvaṉa viṟaliruñ ciṉattaṉa</l>
<l>vēḻaṅkaḷ tuyarkkūra</l>
<l>pilaṅkoḷ vāḷeyiṟ ṟariyavai tiritaru</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where resides the god who made ash</l>
<l rend="indent">of the great city of Lanka,</l>
<l>Having built a rare stone dam, when the monkey clan performed work</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the dark sea churned,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where aimlessly wander</l>
<l rend="indent">lions with dagger[-like] teeth in their cavernous [maws],</l>
<l>So that the anxiety of mountain-like, wild, victorious, dark, angry elephants</l>
<l rend="indent">is acute.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
